properties.name: Unearthly Routes
properties.description:
So you have your usual routes and your unusual routes, and when neither of those will do, you have your unearthly routes - the ones that don't make any sense except in relation to some abstract gradient or ghostly bit of infrastructure. Oh come now, you don't think that infrastructure can have a ghost or a soul; you don't think it can haunt you? Oh, but it can.
